# Enterprise SIEM System

A comprehensive Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) system designed for enterprise environments. This SIEM provides real-time security monitoring, threat detection, incident response, and compliance reporting capabilities.

## Project Structure (Updated)

```
security.operations.center/
├── src/                    # Source code
│   ├── siem/               # Core SIEM components
│   │   ├── core/           # Core framework and base classes
│   │   ├── services/       # Service implementations
│   │   ├── models/         # Data models
│   │   ├── api/            # API endpoints and handlers
│   │   └── utils/          # Utility functions
│   │
│   ├── edr/                # Endpoint Detection & Response
│   ├── dlp/                # Data Loss Prevention
│   ├── hips/               # Host-based IPS
│   ├── nips/               # Network-based IPS
│   ├── ndr/                # Network Detection & Response
│   └── fim/                # File Integrity Monitoring
│
├── tests/                  # Test files
│   ├── unit/               # Unit tests
│   ├── integration/        # Integration tests
│   └── e2e/                # End-to-end tests
│
├── config/                 # Configuration files
│   ├── development/        # Development configurations
│   ├── production/         # Production configurations
│   └── testing/            # Testing configurations
│
├── docs/                   # Documentation
│   ├── api/                # API documentation
